Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.88,0:08:57.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開什麼玩笑！？  為什麼會追過來啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.50,0:09:58.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他只是我的同班同學而已 不是你所想的那樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.06,0:10:01.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.19,0:10:13.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,男子高中生的日常！？

Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.59,0:10:20.60,Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs60\blur12\fad(700,800)\shad0\3a&H01&\c&HFCFBFD&\pos(369,579)\shad0\3c&H4B42BB&}男子高中生與煮年糕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.87,0:11:05.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,！？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.53,0:11:20.24,Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs43\bord3\fad(500,500)\fn華康超黑體\shad0\3a&H01&\3c&HE4EBEB&\c&H0101C5&\pos(631,710)}※年 糕 請 仔 細 的 咀 嚼 再 慢 慢 的 吞 進 嘴 裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.86,0:11:19.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}正... 正月裡吃年糕 結果噎著啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.22,0:11:24.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想求救 但是家裡的人都出去旅遊了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.59,0:11:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰... 來 救 救 我 啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.30,0:11:33.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吉竹... 吉竹！！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.12,0:11:47.89,Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs43\bord3\fad(500,500)\fn華康超黑體\shad0\3a&H01&\3c&HE4EBEB&\c&H0101C5&\pos(631,710)}※年 糕 請 仔 細 的 咀 嚼 再 慢 慢 的 吞 進 嘴 裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.30,0:11:41.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,！？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.91,0:11:45.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}年糕卡在喉嚨裡了啊！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.40,0:11:47.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}啊... 誰... 誰來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.34,0:11:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,忠邦 救我...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.46,0:12:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}！？
